 * Tested on:
 *  + GLIBC 2.39 (x86_64, x86 & aarch64)
 *  + GLIBC 2.34 (x86_64, x86 & aarch64)
 *  + GLIBC 2.31 (x86_64, x86 & aarch64)
 *  + GLIBC 2.27 (x86_64, x86 & aarch64)
