     * (`++counts[tc_index]`) at `0x5555555596b8`: 
     * delta = 0x5555555596b8 - (&tcache->counts) = 0x5555555596b8 - 0x555555559010 = 0x6a8
     * Even if ASLR is on, the delta would always be `0x6a8`. So no heap-leak is required.
    */

